title: Night of the Blood Beast (1958 Sci-Fi) Moonlit carnage. Creature unleashed. No escape.

sources.title: Night of the Blood Beast (1958 Sci-Fi) Moonlit carnage. Creature unleashed. No escape.
sources.description:
An astronaut crashes back to Earth—dead. But surprise! His body is now seeded with rapidly gestating alien embryos. Cue a team of scientists (including his fiancée) battling a bloodsucking space monster with a very proactive approach to interspecies diplomacy.  No girl was safe as long as this head-hunting thing roamed the land!

Alternative titles: The Creature from Galaxy 27 (1958) 

Directed by Bernard L. Kowalski

Producer: Roger Corman
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL2gsu7VGzgdYLD4ZQC1D1o3WC_ePvnOng
Writers: Gene Corman, Martin Varno
Stars: Michael Emmet, Angela Greene, John Baer, Ed Nelson

Genres: Horror, Sci-Fi
Budget:  $68k, shot in 7 days.
Release date: December 1958
